        "desc": "<p>從蘭那羅的故事中得到的果實。其中蘊含著戰勝任何危機的潛能。</p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/08/30/7998136/0e1cecaeba7b12c8c9adcb2f11eccd5e_5762184244019785700.png",
